Mouse 1  1  A  Function "CloseWindow"
Mouse 2  1	A  All ($c) Close
Mouse 3  1  A  Destroy

Mouse 1  2  A  Function "MaximizeWindow"
Mouse 2  2  A  MaximizeToSide -0
Mouse 3  2  A  MaximizeToSide +0

Mouse 1  4  A  IconifyWindow
Mouse 3  4  A  Maximize

